OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening rain
OL,6,Facross Scotland moves south, reaching
OL,7,Fcentral areas by dawn. Showers follow,
OL,8,Fbecoming a little wintry over the
OL,9,Fmountains of Scotland. Clear spells
OL,10,Felsewhere, but turning cold for the
OL,11,Ftime of year, with a risk of a rural
OL,12,Ffrost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FCloud and rain continues
OL,15,Fsouthwards, clearing the UK into the
OL,16,Fevening. Sunny spells elsewhere, but a
OL,17,Ffew showers over northern Scotland and
OL,18,Feastern coasts of England, where
OL,19,Fbreezy. Below-average temperatures.
